<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="no">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Khanpro Transport - Priser</title>

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    html,
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      width: 100%;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      background: #ffffff;
      color: #0b1220;
    }

    .kp-price-info,
    .kp-price-info * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .kp-price-info {
      padding: 110px 24px;
      background: #ffffff;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      color: #0b1220;
    }

    .kp-price-info__inner {
      max-width: 1150px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .kp-price-info__label {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: rgba(11,18,32,0.58);
    }

    .kp-price-info h2 {
      margin: 0 0 24px;
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5.4vw, 5rem);
      line-height: 1;
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: -0.055em;
      color: #050505;
    }

    .kp-price-info__lead {
      max-width: 840px;
      margin: 0 auto 48px;
      font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 1.8vw, 1.35rem);
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: rgba(11,18,32,0.72);
    }

    .kp-price-info__grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .kp-price-info__card {
      padding: 30px 24px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      background: #ffffff;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 36px rgba(11,18,32,0.07);
      border: 1px solid rgba(11,18,32,0.06);
      transition: transform 0.35s ease, box-shadow 0.35s ease;
    }

    .kp-price-info__card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-8px);
      box-shadow: 0 24px 52px rgba(11,18,32,0.13);
    }

    .kp-price-info__card h3 {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      font-size: 1.08rem;
      line-height: 1.2;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #0b1220;
    }

    .kp-price-info__card p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 0.94rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: rgba(11,18,32,0.68);
    }

    .kp-price-info__box {
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 0 auto 30px;
      padding: 22px 24px;
      border-radius: 22px;
      background: rgba(11,18,32,0.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(11,18,32,0.06);
      display: grid;
      gap: 7px;
    }

    .kp-price-info__box strong {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #0b1220;
    }

    .kp-price-info__box span {
      font-size: 0.94rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: rgba(11,18,32,0.68);
    }

    .kp-price-info__actions {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
      max-width: 430px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .kp-price-info__btn {
      min-height: 52px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #0b1220;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 0.94rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease, background 0.3s ease;
    }

    .kp-price-info__btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 16px 30px rgba(11,18,32,0.18);
      background: #111827;
    }

    .kp-price-info__btn--ghost {
      background: transparent;
      color: #0b1220;
      border: 1px solid rgba(11,18,32,0.25);
    }

    .kp-price-info__btn--ghost:hover {
      background: rgba(11,18,32,0.05);
      box-shadow: none;
    }

    @media (max-width: 850px) {
      .kp-price-info {
        padding: 72px 16px;
      }

      .kp-price-info h2 {
        font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 10vw, 3.6rem);
        letter-spacing: -0.06em;
      }

      .kp-price-info__lead {
        margin-bottom: 36px;
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      .kp-price-info__grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 16px;
      }

      .kp-price-info__card {
        padding: 24px 20px;
      }

      .kp-price-info__actions {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 520px) {
      .kp-price-info {
        padding: 64px 14px;
      }

      .kp-price-info__actions {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        max-width: 100%;
      }

      .kp-price-info__btn {
        width: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <section class="kp-price-info">
    <div class="kp-price-info__inner">

      <span class="kp-price-info__label">Priser</span>

      <h2>Hva koster flytting og transport?</h2>

      <p class="kp-price-info__lead">
        Prisen avhenger av type oppdrag, mengde, avstand, etasje, bærehjelp og hvor mye tid jobben tar. Derfor gir vi alltid et tilpasset tilbud basert på behovene dine.
      </p>

      <div class="kp-price-info__grid">
        <div class="kp-price-info__card">
          <h3>Små oppdrag</h3>
          <p>Perfekt for enkel bortkjøring, småflytting eller transport av enkelte møbler.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="kp-price-info__card">
          <h3>Flytteoppdrag</h3>
          <p>Pris beregnes etter omfang, bærehjelp, avstand og tidsbruk.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="kp-price-info__card">
          <h3>Bedrift &amp; kontor</h3>
          <p>Vi lager en plan og gir tilbud basert på størrelse, utstyr og ønsket tidspunkt.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="kp-price-info__box">
        <strong>Få et raskt prisoverslag</strong>
        <span>Send oss noen detaljer om oppdraget, så gir vi deg et uforpliktende tilbud.</span>
      </div>

      <div class="kp-price-info__actions">
        <a href="https://khanprotransport.no/kontakt-oss2" class="kp-price-info__btn">Få prisoverslag</a>
        <a href="tel:+4740610527" class="kp-price-info__btn kp-price-info__btn--ghost">Ring oss</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</body>
</html>
